---
name: 7-Day Trial System
description: New users get 7-day free trial with limited features, dynamic countdown banner, upgrade push
type: feature
---
- Trial duration: 7 days from signup
- Status: trialing → expired (after 7 days) or active (after upgrade)
- Allowed: 150 CRM contacts, unlimited bookings, AI Calendar, 20 AI Pricing uses, 10 AI follow-ups
- Restricted: Advanced AI CRM, Voice assistant, White-label, Multi-team
- TrialBanner component shows dynamic messages based on days remaining
- useTrialLimits hook provides feature gating limits
- After expiry: restricted access with upgrade message
